                     <interp inst="t17910413-63-off358" type="offenceSubcategory" value="grandLarceny"></interp>
               feloniously stealing, on the <rs id="t17910413-63-cd359" type="crimeDate">31st of March</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17910413-63-off358 t17910413-63-cd359"></join>, five silver tea-spoons, value 4 s. a silver sugar-tongs, value 12 d.
            </rs> the goods of 
               
                  <persName id="t17910413-63-victim728" type="victimName">
                     Isaac 
                     Elsgood
                  <interp inst="t17910413-63-victim728" type="surname" value="Elsgood"></interp>
